    <comment>- updated to 2.20.0 (2.02)
   see /usr/share/doc/packages/perl-Graphics-Toolkit-Color/Changes
  2.02    2026-03-30   lichtkind
  -------
      * = minor feature release
      * + add method 'apply' with only argument 'gamma'
      * + add argument 'only' to method 'invert', selecting axis to invert</comment>
